CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 25, 1959, pg. 14 reads: "Paper Counter (Filing Department) - Left to right: Fred Owens, floor clerk; Thomas Rae, writ clerk, and John B. Crigler, clerk."
TitMainTitle: Clerks Fred Owens, Thomas Rae, and John B. Crigler with documents in Allegheny County Prothonotary Office
